OL,3,CMerseyside clubs unite to condemn
OL,4,Cracist abuse of Doucoure after derby
OL,6,FEverton and Liverpool have united in
OL,7,Fcondemning racist abuse directed
OL,8,Ftowards Abdoulaye Doucoure after the
OL,9,Ffinal Merseyside Derby at Goodison
OL,10,FPark.
OL,12,FThe Mali international and Curtis
OL,13,FJones were sent off for second
OL,14,Fbookable offences following the final
OL,15,Fwhistle after scuffling, when the Reds
OL,16,Fmidfielder took exception to his
OL,17,Fopponent's celebrations in front of
OL,18,Fvisiting fans, in reaction to James
OL,19,FTarkowski's equaliser in the eighth
OL,20,Fminute of added time.
