OL,3,CMerseyside clubs unite to condemn
OL,4,Cracist abuse of Doucoure after derby
OL,6,FDoucoure was subsequently targeted
OL,7,Fwith abuse on social media after the 2-
OL,8,F2 Premier League draw.
OL,10,F"Everton and Liverpool Football Clubs
OL,11,Fare aware of ` and condemn in the
OL,12,Fstrongest possible terms ` racist
OL,13,Fabuse received by Abdoulaye Doucoure
OL,14,Ffollowing Wednesday night's Merseyside
OL,15,Fderby," said a joint statement by the
OL,16,Ftwo clubs.
OL,18,F"Such abuse is reprehensible and will
OL,19,Fnot, and should not, be tolerated.
