OL,3,CMerseyside clubs unite to condemn
OL,4,Cracist abuse of Doucoure after derby
OL,6,F"Together, the two clubs will work
OL,7,Fwith Merseyside Police who are
OL,8,Fconducting an investigation with the
OL,9,Faim of identifying the individuals
OL,10,Fresponsible.
OL,12,F"We also encourage people who witness
OL,13,For experience online abuse to report
OL,14,Fand highlight it to the social media
OL,15,Fplatforms on which it appears.
OL,17,F"We must all, including the social
OL,18,Fmedia companies, take a zero-tolerance
OL,19,Fstance. Platforms need to take
OL,20,Faccountability and action to ban such
OL,21,Fabusers.
