OL,3,CMerseyside clubs unite to condemn
OL,4,Cracist abuse of Doucoure after derby
OL,6,F"Racism and hate has no place online,
OL,7,Fin our stadia or in our communities."
OL,9,FMerseyside Police appealed for any
OL,10,Finformation which may identify those
OL,11,Fresponsible.
OL,13,F"We are investigating this and take
OL,14,Fthese reports of hate crime extremely
OL,15,Fseriously," said Chief Superintendent
OL,16,FClaire Doyle.
OL,18,F"If you have any information in
OL,19,Frelation please let us know because it
OL,20,Fcould help our ongoing enquiries.
