OL,3,CMerseyside clubs unite to condemn
OL,4,Cracist abuse of Doucoure after derby
OL,6,F"We have successfully prosecuted so-
OL,7,Fcalled fans for racist abuse and they
OL,8,Fhave been handed football banning
OL,9,Forders along with a criminal record
OL,10,Ffor their behaviour.
OL,12,F"Merseyside Police will not tolerate
OL,13,Fhate crime in any form and is working
OL,14,Fto identify and bring to justice
OL,15,Fanyone found responsible for
OL,16,Fcommitting it."
OL,18,FBut overall police praised matchgoing
OL,19,Ffans for their behaviour, with just
OL,20,Feight arrests made inside and outside
OL,21,Fthe ground.
