OL,3,CMerseyside clubs unite to condemn
OL,4,Cracist abuse of Doucoure after derby
OL,6,F"It was a great atmosphere last night
OL,7,Fwith high emotions on both sides and
OL,8,Ffans enjoyed themselves responsibly,
OL,9,Fseeing the Grand Old Lady off in
OL,10,Fstyle," added Chief Superintendent
OL,11,FDoyle.
OL,13,F"I would like to thank everyone for
OL,14,Fenjoying the evening safely, as there
OL,15,Fwere very little incidents to note
OL,16,Fwith the vast majority of football
OL,17,Ffans enjoying the game without causing
OL,18,Fany disruption."
